ure this is a universal problem with all activated abilities.  Perhaps Nexus Gate and Exodus do not have these problems since they do not require a target, but I know Manaburn and several other targetable abilities for other classes experience this problem. <p><table><tr><td><center><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=67917"><font text-decoration=none size=2>Zaul En'Taro</a></font><br><font size=-2> Wizard Extraordinaire </b></font></tr></td></table></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/urombusmindspire.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Rombus Mindspire</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle><table width=111><tr><td style=filter:glow(color=#6633FF strength=1);font-family:arial;font-weight;bold;font-size:'1pt' nowrap><font size=1 color=#FFFFFF face=Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif>Forum Sorcerer</font></td></tr></table><table width=111><tr><td style=filter:glow(color=#6633FF strength=1);font-family:arial;font-weight;bold;font-size:'1pt' nowrap><font size=1 color=#FFFFFF face=Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif>NOT Rhombus!</font></td></tr></table></span><br>  Posts: 2998<br> <font color=#ffffff>(1/21/02 8:06 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Manaburn and other activated AA abilities</span><hr size=1> It's a bug with targeted abilities.  Exodus and Nexus gate don't give me any problems, but Mana Burn does.  It's really, really annoying.  I also noticed it's worse in some zones than others as well. <p><br>
